QuestData.Title: Extermination
QuestData.Description: We're sending you in there to clean up this naga infestation. Lethal force has been authorized.$B$BGob Squad will be backing you up on this one, so it should be a cakewalk.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 30 Spitelash Naga in the Ruins of Eldarath.
QuestData.CompletionText: The Gob Squad is famous - nastiest fighters out of all the Wrenchmen. Somehow they manage not to blow themselves up much either, which increases life expectancy a bit.
QuestData.RewardText: Your name's getting around... nearly Gob Squad status some would say. You're a vicious one.
